short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Employed is an employment automation extension for multiple online hiring services, most famously indeed.com and linked.com.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Employed is an employment automation extension for multiple online hiring services, most famously indeed.com and linked.com.

Employed Limited:
Applies to 25 non-form based job applications

Employed Unlimited
Applies to 100 form and non-form based job applications
